\b\fs28 NBIO DPM Control = \cf6 Manual                             \b0\fs22\lang1036                                                                                         \cf0\fs24\lang12 Sets Northbridge I/O Dynamic Power Management to manual, keeping performance levels fixed. This avoids delays or latency spikes caused by automatic frequency scaling during data transfers.\par
