\b\f2\fs28 Discrete GPU's Audio = \cf6 Disabled  \cf0\b0\i\f0\lang1036 (\fs22 recommended, only if you dont use it\fs28 )\f2\lang12                 \b\i0                          \b0\fs24 Disables the HDMI/DisplayPort audio output capability of the discrete GPU. If you don\rquote t use GPU audio, disabling it removes unnecessary audio device enumeration and processing, slightly reducing driver overhead and simplifying the Windows audio device list.\f0\fs22\par
